li id=\"cite_note-5\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-5\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"> <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Hendrik Baier</a> (<b>2010</b>). <i>Adaptive Playout Policies for Monte-Carlo Go</i>. Master's thesis, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/University_of_Osnabr%C3%BCck\">University of Osnabrück</a>, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.ke.tu-darmstadt.de/lehre/arbeiten/master/2010/Baier_Hendrik.pdf\">pdf</a></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-6\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-6\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Connect_Four\">Connect Four from Wikipedia</a></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-7\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-7\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://hendrikbaier.jimdo.com/publications/\">Publications - Hendrik Baier's website</a></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-8\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-8\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://dblp.uni-trier.de/pers/hd/b/Baier:Hendrik\">dblp: Hendrik Baier</a></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-9\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-9\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://groups.google.com/d/msg/computer-go-archive/AtJamp8wxSM/QfKf-y1fSQMJ\">Re: [Computer-go</a> Computer-go Digest, Vol 12, Issue 79] by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Hendrik Baier</a>, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://groups.google.com/forum/#!forum/computer-go-archive\">Computer Go Archive</a>, January 26, 2011</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-10\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-10\">↑</a></span> 